item.title: Im logged in
item.dc:creator: @Joe_w000 Joe w000

-Joe.

item.title: Im logged in
item.dc:creator: @runescapekid runescapekid
item.description:
@runescapekid wrote:

[quote=“Joe w000, post:3, topic:91198”]Well, Make a new account and log in, If it works, Try your old account again. Then, If the other account works, ask the owner to delete your account and then re-mod it and add the stats again. That’s how I help my members and they always get there problems sorted.

  • Joe.[/quote]

yes that usually works, if not come back to it after a while or refresh the browser
